ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
mayors who take their salary in Bitcoin</a>, and she objected to the practi=
ce because a Bitcoin is so expensive. =E2=80=9CDoes Eric Adams even get a w=
hole Bitcoin for his salary,=E2=80=9D she asked skeptically, and no he does=
 not.[2] I found this a strange objection. Bitcoin trades in <a href=3D"htt=
ps://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26573728.257620/aHR0cHM6Ly9lbi5i=
aXRjb2luLml0L3dpa2kvU2F0b3NoaV8odW5pdCk/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBdff770cc" =
