uite respectably, traditionally stupid.</p><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">It =
is so traditional, in fact, that the stupidest investor who cares about nom=
inal stock prices is the Dow:</p><blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">A=
